'''何塞·佩德羅·巴爾馬塞特·帕斯卡'''（{{lang-es|Jose Pedro Balmaceda Pascal}}，{{bd|1975年|4月2日}}）或簡稱'''佩德羅·帕斯卡'''（{{lang-es|Pedro Pascal}}），是一位[[智利|智利]]裔[[美國|美國]]男演員。他最著名的是在[[HBO|HBO]]電視劇《[[冰與火之歌：權力遊戲|冰與火之歌：權力遊戲]]》（2014年）[[权力的游戏_(第四季)|第四季]]中所飾演的{{le|奧柏倫·馬泰爾|Oberyn Martell}}<ref name="Wetpaint 29 June 2013">{{cite news|last=Martin|first=Rebecca|title=Who Is Pedro Pascal? 5 Things to Know About Oberyn Martell Actor|url=http://www.wetpaint.com/game-of-thrones/articles/2013-06-28-who-is-pedro-pascal-oberyn|accessdate=2013-06-30|newspaper={{le|Wetpaint|Wetpaint}}|date=2013-06-29|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106233111/http://www.wetpaint.com/game-of-thrones/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及在[[Netflix|Netflix]]原創電視劇《[[毒梟_(電視劇)|毒梟]]》（2015年至2017年）中飾演的哈維爾·潘納一角。

2019年起，帕斯卡於[[Disney+|Disney+]]電視劇《[[曼達洛人_(電視劇)|曼達洛人]]》中擔任主演。

== 早期生活 ==
帕斯卡出生於[[智利|智利]]的[[聖地亞哥_(智利)|聖地亞哥]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Ito|first=Robert|title=A Lethal Prince, Even if a Bit Clumsy: Pedro Pascal Becomes Red Viper on 'Game of Thrones'|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/30/arts/television/pedro-pascal-becomes-red-viper-on-game-of-thrones.html?_r=0|accessdate=2014-05-27|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2014-03-28|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020115/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/30/arts/television/pedro-pascal-becomes-red-viper-on-game-of-thrones.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。帕斯卡的父母是[[薩爾瓦多·阿葉德|薩爾瓦多·阿葉德]]的支持者，並曾參與反對派運動，以反對[[奧古斯圖·皮諾契特|奧古斯圖·皮諾契特]]的軍事獨裁<ref name="reddit">Pascal, Pedro. (2014-05-25). Reddit. [https://www.reddit.com/r/IAmA/comments/26gtvt/i_am_actor_pedro_pascal_i_play_oberyn_in_game_of I am actor Pedro Pascal. I play Oberyn in Game of Thrones, Ask me anything.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.reddit.com/r/IAmA/comments/26gtvt/i_am_actor_pedro_pascal_i_play_oberyn_in_game_of |date=20201110003947 }}</ref>。也因此，他在出生不久後，他的家人在[[丹麥|丹麥]]獲得了政治庇護<ref name=OrangeCoast>{{cite news|last=Broeske|first=Pat H.|title=The Viper Prince|url=http://www.orangecoast.com/features/2014/04/28/the-viper-prince|accessdate=2014-05-27|publisher=Orange Coast|date=2014-04-28|archive-date=2014-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140602035249/http://www.orangecoast.com/features/2014/04/28/the-viper-prince|dead-url=no}}</ref>。帕斯卡主要都是在[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[橙縣_(加利福尼亞州)|橙縣]]和[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[聖安東尼奧_(德克薩斯州)|聖安東尼奧]]成長<ref>{{cite news|last=McIntyre|first=Gina|title='Game of Thrones': Red Viper actor Pedro Pascal hates spoilers too|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/tv/game-of-thrones-red-viper-actor-pedro-pascal-hates-spoilers-too/|accessdate=2014-05-27|newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2014-05-12|archive-date=2018-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908015642/https://herocomplex.latimes.com/tv/game-of-thrones-red-viper-actor-pedro-pascal-hates-spoilers-too/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。帕斯卡在11歲時曾參加了德克薩斯州的國家游泳錦標賽，但在開始主修戲劇後就停止了參與游泳競賽<ref name="reddit"/>。他曾就讀於{{le|奧蘭治縣藝術學院|Orange County School of the Arts}}和[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]的{{le|蒂施藝術學院|Tisch School of the Arts}}，並在[[紐約市|紐約市]]生活了二十多年<ref name=OrangeCoast/>。帕斯卡的弟弟盧卡斯·巴爾馬塞特（Lucas Balmaceda）也是名演員<ref>{{cite web|title=Lucas Balmaceda, el hermano del chileno de Game of Thrones que llegó a remecer Los 80|url=http://www.t13.cl/noticia/entretencion/Lucas-Balmaceda-el-hermano-del-chileno-de-Game-of-Thrones-que-llego-a-remecer-Los-80|website=T13|date=2014-11-12|accessdate=2017-09-22|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111204523/https://www.t13.cl/noticia/entretencion/Lucas-Balmaceda-el-hermano-del-chileno-de-Game-of-Thrones-que-llego-a-remecer-Los-80|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 個人生活 ==
帕斯卡本身能說流利的[[西班牙語|西班牙語]]<ref>{{cite web|title="Narcos" star Pedro Pascal on the mystery of Pablo Escobar's death|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HC5G0bsSQtw|website=YouTube|publisher=CBS|accessdate=2016-09-11|archive-date=2020-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229040511/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HC5G0bsSQtw}}</ref>。他與同在《冰與火之歌：權力遊戲》演出的女演員[[琳娜·海蒂|琳娜·海蒂]]是相當要好的朋友<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latintimes.com/game-thrones-season-4-5-striking-similarities-between-chilean-actor-pedro-pascal-and-his-164663|title=‘Game Of Thrones’ Season 4: 5 Striking Similarities Between Chilean Actor Pedro Pascal And His ‘Red Viper’ Character!|publisher=Latin Times|date=2014-04-09|accessdate=2017-09-22|archive-date=2019-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190425061923/https://www.latintimes.com/game-thrones-season-4-5-striking-similarities-between-chilean-actor-pedro-pascal-and-his-164663|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

帕斯卡和智利候選總統[[加夫列尔·博里奇·丰特|加夫列尔·博里奇·丰特]]親交，亦在[[2021年智利大選|2021年智利大選]]上給予博里奇支持。

